642
00:27:36,140 --> 00:27:37,790
You don't have to worry about that.

643
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:38,610
We'll leave future matters

644
00:27:38,610 --> 00:27:39,500
for the future.

645
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:41,460
Don't do it again.

646
00:27:43,450 --> 00:27:45,460
[Wenzhao Pavilion]

647
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:47,600
This traitor actually makes

648
00:27:47,780 --> 00:27:49,180
a pretty decent teacher.

649
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:05,210
Miss Jiang.

650
00:28:06,900 --> 00:28:07,760
Your Highness.

651
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,580
Are you looking for Her Highness?

652
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:11,310
-She...
-No.

653
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:12,590
I'm here for you.

654
00:28:13,190 --> 00:28:13,850
Miss Jiang,

655
00:28:13,910 --> 00:28:14,950
I don't know what happened

656
00:28:14,950 --> 00:28:15,780
between you and Yan Lin,

657
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:17,460
but he's been acting strangely lately.

658
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:19,680
He used to be the most free-spirited person I know.

659
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:20,310
But now,

660
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:21,440
he's depressed.

661
00:28:21,760 --> 00:28:23,140
He wouldn't tell me anything when I asked him about it.

662
00:28:23,140 --> 00:28:24,270
So I can only ask you.

663
00:28:24,780 --> 00:28:26,580
There are many things in this world

664
00:28:26,580 --> 00:28:28,490
that are difficult to tell others.

665
00:28:28,490 --> 00:28:29,720
If it's convenient for you,

666
00:28:29,720 --> 00:28:32,450
I would like to ask you to pass a message to Yan Lin.

667
00:28:33,430 --> 00:28:34,660
Just tell him that

668
00:28:35,020 --> 00:28:36,820
strong wind shows the strength of grass,

669
00:28:36,820 --> 00:28:38,940
and clouds will part to reveal the moon's glow.

670
00:28:38,940 --> 00:28:39,940
For some matters,

671
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,220
as long as he can keep calm,

672
00:28:41,220 --> 00:28:43,150
things will change for the better.

673
00:28:51,690 --> 00:28:53,700
How ridiculous...

674
00:28:54,860 --> 00:28:55,550
Mr. Wang.

675
00:28:57,930 --> 00:28:58,770
Miss Xue.

