684
00:29:15,900 --> 00:29:17,080
Thank you, Miss Xue.

685
00:29:17,630 --> 00:29:19,910
I deeply appreciate that.

686
00:29:21,250 --> 00:29:23,380
But there is one thing you may not know.

687
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:24,500
During class today,

688
