Junior Preceptor Xie tossed the

689
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:28,050
Book of Etiquettes out of the hall.

690
00:29:28,170 --> 00:29:28,630
This...

691
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:30,470
Why did he...

