797
00:33:49,420 --> 00:33:51,010
Wang Jiu once taught the former emperor.

798
00:33:51,010 --> 00:33:52,300
Although he's a bit old-fashioned,

799
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:54,300
he is the most senior scholar of Hanlin Academy.

800
00:33:54,300 --> 00:33:55,360
It's not that easy.

801
00:33:56,250 --> 00:33:57,810
But my father told me

802
00:33:58,060 --> 00:33:59,700
