820
00:34:46,860 --> 00:34:47,389
Ning'er!

821
00:34:49,510 --> 00:34:50,120
It can't be

822
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:52,080
him, right?

823
00:35:09,810 --> 00:35:11,110
What a coincidence.

824
00:35:12,050 --> 00:35:13,750
Jie, the color of your clothes

