841
00:35:58,870 --> 00:35:59,930
No need to force it.

842
00:36:01,130 --> 00:36:02,120
I have an appointment with Yan Lin.

843
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:03,130
I shall take my leave.

844
00:36:03,130 --> 00:36:03,810
Sit down.

845
00:36:04,140 --> 00:36:05,580
Mother! Mother.

846
00:36:06,420 --> 00:36:07,880
Why are you in such a hurry?

847
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:09,030
